title: Osker - Idle Will Kill
description:
This is a band i REALLY LOVE. California punk at its finest. My friend Steven Hickman turned me onto this back in the late nineties. I am putting this up because i hate when i search for a band on torrent sites and they don&#039;t show up.....ANYWHERE. Not anymore. Never again shall the name OSKER be lost in the shadows of what was the greatest punk movement since the shit started. 

Have fun guys and dolls
